                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Professional Dental Splinting in Nairobi</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 text-lg">Dental splinting is a supportive treatment used to stabilize loose teeth weakened by trauma, gum disease, bone loss, or bite issues.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">By joining affected teeth to stable neighboring teeth, splinting reduces excessive movement and helps improve comfort, chewing ability, and long-term oral stability.</p>
