                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Loose teeth are connected to stable neighboring teeth using a thin, strong material such as composite resin or fiber-reinforced bonding.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">The procedure is minimally invasive and is often completed in a single visit, depending on how many teeth need support.</p>
